From 3ba1e2685f89bcd631b66748f70f69a5eecf741b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Brian Neradt <brian.neradt@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 23 Jul 2024 17:22:20 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] proxy.config.http.drop_chunked_trailers (#11603)

This adds the proxy.config.http.drop_chunked_trailers configuration that
allows dropping of chunked trailers.
---
